{"tid":1992283,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"屬於中国人的籠子要來了 steam中国版即將到來","createTime":"2020-04-28T05:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T11:46:43.000Z","uid":21141,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5935f0c0a57c6936858670a8990ededc65125f8d","tid":1992283,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:09:17.000Z","msg":"根據中國關注 Steam 消息的網站「其樂（網站原名稱為「蒸汽動力」)」引述一名網友清靈語消息指出，Valve 合作夥伴完美世界已在中國取得 Steam 平台相關域名與證書，其中「wmsjsteam」（完美世界 Steam）早在今年 2 月就取得了證書，並由 Valve 所擁有。<br />\n <br />\n　　中國遊戲廠商完美世界於前年與 Valve 宣布合作展開 Steam 中國版計畫，去年 8 月宣布 Steam 中國版將定名為蒸汽平台，如今傳出蒸汽平台相關域名等都已經通過審核。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友發現，「wmsjsteam」相關域名在今年 4 月 9 日已經通過審核，而包括完美世界對戰平台系統、支付、數據分析、內容審核後台、神秘商店等系統都在去年 12 月獲得軟體著作權。<br />\n <br />\n　　此消息傳出後，像是北京新浪網、17173 等媒體都猜測 Steam 中國版可能即將到來，或許可望在今年正式上線。<br />\n <br />\n外掛可以用來中国人打中国人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2744b586084eab30af7f19314391412ba3f298","tid":1992283,"uid":21141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=196098\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D196098&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPoc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=2cdb029d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=196098</a>"},{"pid":"f9602cb282321b8e9cabf6788eb0bfeb4f620d54","tid":1992283,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5440c0c63a05f8be1b28bfd466fddba23041d13f","tid":1992283,"uid":234310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"成班支那人又咪用vpn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620110fb1734d10bf66ff